{"id":571,"date":"2017-03-10T21:08:13","date_gmt":"2017-03-10T21:08:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/?p=571"},"modified":"2018-07-27T11:21:23","modified_gmt":"2018-07-27T11:21:23","slug":"create-proposal","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/create-proposal\/","title":{"rendered":"Create proposal"},"content":{"rendered":"<h4><strong>Create a proposal<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>From the main menu navigate to Sales-&gt;Proposals and on the top left side click the\u00a0<strong>Create Proposal <\/strong>button<\/p>\n<p>You can<strong> create a proposal to lead or to a customer.<\/strong><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Choose Related to Lead or Customer.<\/li>\n<li>Choose which <strong>lead\/customer is related<\/strong>. On the right side, the found information will be auto-filled. You can adjust according to your needs.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Status\u00a0&#8211;<\/strong>\u00a0By default, the draft status will be auto-selected. Note that proposals with draft status are not visible to customers, also the proposal &#8220;Open&#8221; status means that is open for the customer to make actions e.q. accept or decline the proposal<\/li>\n<li><strong>Open Till<\/strong> &#8211; The date when the proposal will stay open and the user can take actions (Accept\/Decline) &#8211; Go to <strong>Setup-&gt;Settings-&gt;Finance-&gt;Proposal<\/strong> to set <strong>Proposal due after<\/strong> to auto to populate this field.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Currency<\/strong> &#8211; When creating a proposal to lead you are allowed to add any currency you need otherwise if you are creating a proposal for a customer the system base <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/currencies\/\">currency <\/a>will be used or the <a href=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/currencies\/\">customer currency<\/a>.<\/li>\n<li>Allow Comments &#8211; If this field is unchecked the user won&#8217;t be able to comment on the proposal ex. Negotiate with price etc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Save the proposal to add proposal content.<\/p>\n<h4><strong>Add proposal content<\/strong><\/h4>\n<p>You can add proposal content directly from the admin area while previewing the proposal.<\/p>\n<p>After saving\/creating the proposal you will be redirected to the preview area where you can add content.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-3941 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-1024x782.png\" alt=\"Add Proposal Content\" width=\"980\" height=\"748\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-1024x782.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-300x229.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-768x587.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-60x46.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-150x115.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content.png 1029w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>By default the proposal content will contain only a merge field <strong>{proposal_items}<\/strong>, this merge field will output the proposal items e.q. in PDF or when a customer is viewing the proposal HTML area.<\/p>\n<p>If you need to add additional content, just click in the editor and start typing.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-large wp-image-3942\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank-1024x364.png\" alt=\"Proposal Content Blank\" width=\"980\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank-1024x364.png 1024w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank-300x107.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank-768x273.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank-60x21.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank-150x53.png 150w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-content-blank.png 1025w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>The proposal content will be auto-saved, you don&#8217;t need to perform save, however, if it&#8217;s needed you can use the shortcut\u00a0<strong>CTRL+S<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4>Merge Fields<\/h4>\n<p>To prevent creating the same content, again and again, you can use the merge fields feature by clicking on the link <strong>Available Merge\u00a0Fields <\/strong>and when you will need to create new similar proposal you need to copy the existing one.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-573 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-2available-merge-feilds-proposal-768x431-300x168.png\" alt=\"merge proposal\" width=\"693\" height=\"388\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-2available-merge-feilds-proposal-768x431-300x168.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-2available-merge-feilds-proposal-768x431.png 768w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-2available-merge-feilds-proposal-768x431-60x34.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-2available-merge-feilds-proposal-768x431-150x84.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 693px) 100vw, 693px\" \/><\/p>\n<h4>Copy Proposal<\/h4>\n<p>To copy the proposal click\u00a0on\u00a0<strong>More<\/strong> and click on <strong>Copy<\/strong>.<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-574 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-3copy-proposal-300x293-300x293.png\" alt=\"copy proposal\" width=\"358\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-3copy-proposal-300x293.png 300w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-3copy-proposal-300x293-60x60.png 60w, https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/03\/proposal-3copy-proposal-300x293-150x147.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 358px) 100vw, 358px\" \/><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Create a proposal From the main menu navigate to Sales-&gt;Proposals and on the top left side click the\u00a0Create Proposal button You can create a proposal to lead or to a customer. Choose Related to Lead or Customer. Choose which lead\/customer is related. On the right side, the found information will be auto-filled. You can adjust [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[19,16],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-571","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-proposals","category-sales"],"aioseo_notices":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/571","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=571"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/571\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=571"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/help.perfexcrm.com\/wp-json